FB application package is a simple to use PHP package that will allow you to quickly deploy a versioned Facebook application for Likers and Non-Likers.

You will need to adjust a few settings in the following files.

index.php
- replace APPID
- replace APP_SECRET

footer.php
- replace APPID

To Deploy - 
Download FB application package and unzip
create a folder on your server for example www.example.com/facebook
place all of the files from FB application package in this folder.
Create an application on Facebook and point the Canvas URL to your URL
Once you've done this you're ready to rock and roll! 

here's a working demo http://www.facebook.com/apps/application.php?id=1776741342290105&sk=app_1776741342290105